                        <p>Deepen your leadership and directorship skills with our wide-range of <b><span style="color: #1AA9E1;">director development programmes</span></b>, held in-person, virtually or both. <a href="https://pulse.icdm.com.my/programmes-overview/programme-calendar/">View calendar</a> or email <a href="mailto:zefry@icdm.com.my;development@icdm.com.my">Zefry</a>.</p>
                        <p>Tap on our expertise to design an <b><span style="color: #1AA9E1;">in-house bespoke programme</span></b> that suits your organisation’s unique requirements. Email <a href="mailto:jackie@icdm.com.my;haniza@icdm.com.my;">Jackie</a>.</p>
                        <p>Meet your Malaysian Code of Corporate Governance (MCCG) needs with a candid and objective-driven <b><span style="color: #1AA9E1;">board & director effectiveness evaluation</span></b>. Email <a href="mailto:haniza@icdm.com.my;development@icdm.com.my">Haniza.</a></p>
